         The problem i have with Funeral Pyre only dropping off Rhag2 is this:</P><P>If you are in a guild that is capable of killing High Priest, Arch Lich, Cursed and Emperor, then there is very little priority to go after Rhag2.  Sure, Rhag2 can drop GRC and other useful spells that your guild will want and NEED for fights in Luclin, but none of his other loots are worthy of putting something like Cursed or Creator on the backburner.  And furthermore, GRC drops off of lots of other mobs that DO take a higher priority for guilds like the ones i am describing.</P><P>So, for someone like myself who is in a guild capable of killing all the above mentioned mobs, yet still has not had more than 2 opportunities to even kill Rhag2 since Luclin was released, what am i to do?  Rhag1 and Rhag2 are killed regularly by other guilds on my server as well, its not like they just sit there waiting for my guild to be done killing Cursed and High Priest.</P><P>Basically i have pretty given up hope on getting Funeral Pyre.  The only way i will see it is on the rare time my guild is in Ssra, Rhag2 is up AND NOTHING ELSE AT ALL WORTHY OF KILLING IS UP ANYWHERE IN LUCLIN, AND i can convince everyone that we really do need to try to get yet another copy of GRC or some sh!t.  Because believe me, convincing them we need another copy of Funeral Pyre is not going to fly.</P><P>For Christ's sake, why can't they just make it so there is a teeny tiny bit of randomness to which mobs can drop these spells ( not just FP )???  Is someone gonna give birth because the Emperor drops Funeral Pyre instead of Uberwizziespell?  I think not.</P><P>I would really like to see these spells that are currently only dropping off of one specific boss mob in Luclin to be spread out over a wider range of boss mobs.  I feel this would even up the playing field for people in a large way, not making them any more accessible than they are now, not increasing their rate of entry into the world, just introducing a bit of randomness to their entry that does not exist at the moment.</P><P>Vtyn</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
